ROME, Italy, February 24, 2020/APO Group/ --
                                                        
                            The Farnesina has been following from the very beginning the matter of the Italian plane grounded in Mauritius, in constant contact with Alitalia airline and the Embassy in Pretoria, responsible for this area, in order to ensure maximum assistance to Italians on board.



                            
                        
                    
                    
                    
                                            Distributed by APO Group on behalf of Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Italy.